::Fidgit/KitKat::

A stasis lands.  A Canine figure jumps out of the pod. She looks about and 
runs through the trees.  She hoped that no one saw the pod land.  She ran 
through the forest looking for a spot to hide in.  She stopped and sniffed 
the air.  She smelled other wolves in the area.  Two males to be exact. This 
made her nervious.  She ran untill she came to a lake.  She didn't see 
anyone and went to the waters edge.  She started to drink when something 
moved in the water. She jumped back.  An otter poked it's head from the 
water's surface and looked at the canine bot.

Fidgit: "Hello, how are you?"

KitKat: "I'm well."

Fidgit: "That's good to hear.  I'm Fidgit.  I'm a Maximal.  Who are you?"

KitKat: "My name is KitKat,  I'm a...a.." she looked at the symbol on her 
arm and looked back at the otter. "I'm not sure.  The crash rattled me a 
bit.  What is this symbol on my shoulder?"

Fidgit: She looked at the symbol. "Oh my, that's not a maximal symbol.  
That's a Predacon symbol."

KitKat: "Oh. Well then, I guess I should be on my way then."  With that she 
walked off into the forest.

Fidgit: She watched as the wolf walked away.  She wondered how a nice bot 
can be a Predacon.  After all, it wasn't everyday that a Maximal and a 
Predacon have a civil conversation.  She dove back into the water and swam 
to her spark's content.
